# The Vite config safely maps these public values into browser code if the VITE_* variants are absent:
# EPIC_NON_PROD_CLIENT_ID -> VITE_EPIC_CLIENT_ID
# CERNER_CLIENT_ID -> VITE_CERNER_CLIENT_ID
# EPIC_SANDBOX_BASE_URL -> VITE_EPIC_SANDBOX_BASE_URL
# CERNER_SANDBOX_BASE_URL -> VITE_CERNER_SANDBOX_BASE_URL
# Epic sandbox redirect URI is intentionally VITE-only. The known accepted local value is http://localhost:3000 with no trailing slash.

